<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Welcome to our Terms and Conditions page. Here you will find the basic terms and conditions for renting a car from us.</p>

<h2>Payment and Reservation</h2>
<p>After making a reservation, you will receive an email with a link to choose your payment method and further steps such as the pick-up method, pick-up time, and a deposit of 300 PLN.</p>

<h2>General Terms</h2>
<ul>
    <li>All rentals require a deposit of 300 PLN.</li>
    <li>Payment can be made through the link provided in the reservation email.</li>
    <li>Pick-up and drop-off times must be confirmed in advance.</li>
    <li>Any damage to the vehicle must be reported immediately.</li>
    <li>Failure to return the vehicle on time may result in additional charges.</li>
	<li>Smoking is not allowed in the vehicle.</li>
	<li>Animals are not allowed in the vehicle.</li>
	<li>Only the person who made the reservation is allowed to drive the vehicle.</li>
	<li>Any traffic violations or fines incurred during the rental period are the responsibility of the driver.</li>
	<li>The vehicle must be returned with a full tank of fuel.</li>
</ul>

<p>Thank you for choosing our car rental service. We look forward to serving you!</p>